# Changelog - gateway-tools

## 2026-01-15 - Initial Creation

**Type:** Gateway (routing index)
**Location:** `.claude/skills/gateway-tools/`

### Created

- Gateway skill created for tools domain
- Routes to library paths: `.claude/skill-library/tools/*`
- Categories: Audio/Video Tools, Docker Tools, CLI Utilities, System Tools
- Initial skills: 1 skill (transcribing-audio)

### Purpose

Provides intent-based routing to tool wrapper skills in the library. Enables discovery of:
- Audio/video processing tools (transcription, recording, conversion)
- Docker-based utilities (containerized tools)
- CLI wrappers (command-line tool integration)
- System-level utilities (file processing, system tools)

### Initial Routing Table

**Audio/Video Tools:**
- transcribing-audio - Docker/Whisper transcription wrapper

**Docker Tools:**
- transcribing-audio - Whisper CLI via Docker

**CLI Utilities:**
- transcribing-audio - Whisper command-line interface

**System Tools:**
- (Future expansion: audio recording, video processing, file conversion)

### Progressive Disclosure

- Level 1: Routing tables (~200 tokens) - loaded immediately
- Level 2: Skill SKILL.md - loaded on-demand when routed
- Level 3: Skill resources - loaded as-needed during execution

### Cross-Gateway Integration

Routes to other gateways when tasks involve:
- Testing (gateway-testing)
- Integrations (gateway-integrations)
- Backend (gateway-backend)
- MCP Tools (gateway-mcp-tools)
- Security (gateway-security)

### Future Expansion

Designed to accommodate future tool skills:
- Audio recording capabilities
- Video processing utilities
- File conversion tools
- Image processing
- Document processing
- Database CLI wrappers
- Network diagnostic tools
